Cost、imageUrl。',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-30 11:14:13',0),(2038454860681859074,2038454723398094850,'assistant','观察: 您计划在潮州进行两天游，我为您规划了涵盖主要景点、特色美食和住宿的行程。行程包括广济桥、开元寺、牌坊街等必游景点，安排了潮汕特色美食体验，并提供了住宿建议。整体预算约1000元，适合自由行。请查看详细行程和注意事项。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"destination\": \"潮州\",\n  \"days\": 2,\n  \"budget\": 1000,\n  \"theme\": \"文化古迹探索\",\n  \"dailyPlans\": [\n    {\n      \"day\": 1,\n      \"date\": \"2024-09-01\",\n      \"activities\": [\n        {\n          \"time\": \"morning\",\n          \"name\": \"广济桥\",\n          \"type\": \"attraction\",\n          \"description\": \"中国四大古桥之一，欣赏桥上桥、十八梭船的独特结构\",\n          \"imageUrl\": \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566271757676-72f7a9a2f7a3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80\",\n          \"location\": {\n            \"address\": \"广东省潮州市湘桥区广济桥\",\n            \"longitude\": 116.614976,\n            \"latitude\": 23.679229\n          },\n          \"estimatedCost\": 60,\n          \"tips\": [\"建议早上9点前到达，避开人流高峰\", \"可租借景区讲解器了解历史\"]\n        },\n        {\n          \"time\": \"noon\",\n          \"name\": \"潮汕特色午餐\",\n          \"type\": \"meal\",\n          \"description\": \"品尝潮汕牛肉火锅或砂锅粥等当地特色美食\",\n          \"imageUrl\": \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572635196237-149654504530?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80\",\n          \"location\": {\n            \"address\": \"潮州市湘桥区牌坊街附近餐厅\",\n            \"longitude\": 116.614976,\n            \"latitude\": 23.679229\n          },\n          \"estimatedCost\": 80,\n          \"tips\": [\"推荐尝试潮汕牛肉火锅，鲜美嫩滑\"]\n        },\n        {\n          \"time\": \"evening\",\n          \"name\": \"牌坊街\",\n          \"type\": \"attraction\",\n          \"description\": \"漫步古色古香的牌坊街，感受潮汕文化氛围，品尝夜市小吃\",\n          \"imageUrl\": \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582212707931-77b116d2c2b9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%